OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cburglary victim, 72, dies in hospital
OL,6,FPolice have launched a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation after a man died in
OL,8,Fhospital a month after his Somerset
OL,9,Fhome was burgled.
OL,11,FStephen Ridgeway, 72, told police he
OL,12,Fanswered the door of his property in
OL,13,FTenby Road, Keynsham, in the early
OL,14,Fhours of Sunday 3 November.
OL,16,FHe described how two men forced their
OL,17,Fway inside before assaulting him and
OL,18,Fstealing items including alcohol and
OL,19,Fmobile phones.
