OL,6,FEmergency services were called to Mr
OL,7,FRidgeway's home at around 3am and he
OL,8,Fwas later admitted to hospital, where
OL,9,Fhis condition worsened and he died on
OL,10,FSaturday 7 December.
OL,12,FAvon and Somerset Police said
OL,13,Fpreliminary findings of a post-mortem
OL,14,Fexamination state that the injuries Mr
OL,15,FRidgeway sustained contributed to his
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,FThe case is now being treated as
OL,19,Fmurder by the force's major crime
OL,20,Finvestigation team.
