OL,6,FA man aged in his 30s was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of aggravated burglary
OL,8,Fbefore Mr Ridgeway's death and remains
OL,9,Fon police bail with conditions
OL,10,Fincluding an overnight curfew.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector James
OL,13,FWasiak, who is now leading the
OL,14,Finvestigation, said: "Fast-track
OL,15,Finquiries were carried out immediately
OL,16,Fafter the incident.
