OL,6,F"Colleagues were already following up
OL,7,Fpositive lines of inquiry after the
OL,8,Fearlier appeal and awaiting the
OL,9,Fresults of forensic investigation at
OL,10,Fthe property.
OL,12,F"Since the awful news of the man's
OL,13,Fdeath, we have reviewed that early
OL,14,Fevidence. Today and over the next few
OL,15,Fdays you will see an increased police
OL,16,Fpresence in the area, including
OL,17,Ffurther crime scene investigation at
OL,18,Fthe house.
