OL,6,F"We have found no evidence of any
OL,7,Fwider risk to the community but I'd
OL,8,Furge anyone who has concerns to speak
OL,9,Fwith the neighbourhood policing team,
OL,10,Fwho will be a reassuring uniformed
OL,11,Fpresence while we make these further
OL,12,Finquiries."
OL,14,FMr Ridgeway's family are aware of his
OL,15,Fdeath and will be supported by a
OL,16,Fspecially-trained officer, the force
OL,17,Fconfirmed.
OL,19,FPolice are renewing an earlier appeal
OL,20,Ffor anyone with information or CCTV or
OL,21,Fdashcam footage to come forward.
