OL,6,FMr Wasiak said: "If you were in the
OL,7,FTenby Road area between midnight and
OL,8,F3am that Sunday, November 3, we'd like
OL,9,Fto hear from you.
OL,11,F"You may have noticed something which
OL,12,Fmay not seem important in itself, but
OL,13,Fwhich could be key when connected with
OL,14,Fother information."
OL,16,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,17,Fcall Avon and Somerset Police on 101,
OL,18,Fgiving the reference 5224289518. The
OL,19,Findependent charity Crimestoppers can
OL,20,Fbe contacted anonymously by calling
OL,21,F0800 555 111, or online.
